title: Facing our Inner Demons in Bayonetta 3
description:
Bayonetta is back after a long sabbatical, and now there's like a million of her. Is that too many Bayonettas? Is such a thing possible? Let's find out as we share our thoughts on Bayonetta 3! 

Also discussed: Signalis, Marvel Snap, Idle Acorns, Binding of Isaac, Banshees of Inisherin
author: thebestiesbizemail@gmail.com (Justin McElroy, Griffin McElroy, Chris Plante, Russ Frushtick)
